//
//	Returns:  	integer
//					 1 if it succeeds
//					 0 No Mail Connection or Notification receipients have been set up.
//					-1 if it fails.
//
//	Description:	This function is used to notify the passed in users of the message.
//
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//
//	Revision History
//
